title: Vera van Pol
text: Vera Dorothea Wilhelmina van Pol (born 17 December 1993) is a Dutch <a href="artistic%20gymnast">artistic gymnast</a>, representing her nation in international competitions. She participated in every edition of the <a href="World%20Artistic%20Gymnastics%20Championships">World Championships</a> since <a href="2013%20World%20Artistic%20Gymnastics%20Championships">2013</a>, and eventually finished seventh as a member of the Dutch gymnastics squad in the team all-around tournament at the <a href="2016%20Summer%20Olympics">2016 Summer Olympics</a>.
